&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in design, build, analysis and/or testing of avionics mechanical systems or similar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of experience leading a team of engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project management experience including developing budgets and schedules, and managing resources&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with relevant CAD and analysis tools (NX, ANSYS, Excel, Matlab, or equivalent)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with PCB designers and exposure to PCB layout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands on experience performing fabrication and assembly of components&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proven ability to mentor and coach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mastery of fundamentals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in mechanical or aerospace engineering, or similar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated with strong organizational, written, and oral communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing electronics component packaging and secondary

