&lt;li&gt;0-5 years of professional experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Programming skills in MATLAB or Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong fundamentals in structural dynamics and vibroacoustics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to lead &amp;amp; follow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent oral and written communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
