&lt;li&gt;Own engine as-tested configuration from factory to flight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own test verification activities to ensure accomplished tests meet requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan, prioritize, and execute component (turbopumps, pressure-fed injectors, valves, etc.) and full engine test campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive test data reviews and perform data analysis, own anomaly investigations and resolutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and improve configuration tracking tools, test planning tools, and data reduction and trending tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design build and troubleshoot fluid, mechanical, instrumentation, and control systems for various test applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
