&lt;p&gt;This position is for a 36-week period to start. This period will be split into 3 phases of 12 weeks each. Advancement to the next phase will be considered at the conclusion of each 12-week period. Full-time employment will be considered for each employee at the conclusion of this 36-week period.&lt;/p&gt;
