&lt;li&gt;Partner with cross-functional teams to design features that meet real-world, time-sensitive needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure high performance, reliability, and scalability of visualization tools across both front-end and back-end systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously improve existing tools and develop new features to meet evolving requirements&lt;/li&gt;
