&lt;li&gt;Advanced degree in electrical engineering, physics, or related fields&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous work experience with MIL-STD-461, MIL-STD-464, NASA-STD-4003 documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of in-atmosphere and in-space EMI/EMC including effects of space plasma, charging, grounding, bonding, shielding, design

