&lt;li&gt;Lead all physical security operations for Stoke’s Cape Canaveral facilities, to include operations in Port Canaveral&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement site-specific security strategies aligned with corporate security policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain security plans, post orders, procedures, and operating instructions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct periodic security risk assessments and vulnerability reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee day-to-day security operations and site access control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor security incidents and coordinate response activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage contracted security service providers and guard force personnel&lt;/li&gt;
